<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="18">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$a-ke-meng-de-27" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/a-ke-meng-de-27" class="zg-link" title="阿克萌德">阿克萌德</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$rou-wang-wan" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/rou-wang-wan" class="zg-link" title="柔王丸">柔王丸</a></span>
